Package edu.bu.labs.routing

Record Class Tile

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
edu.bu.labs.routing.Tile
Record Components:
maze - The maze that this tile belongs to.
row - The y coordinate of this tile.
col - The x coordinate of this tile.
state - What is present in this tile (if it is the finish, a wall, etc.)
public record Tile(Maze maze, int row, int col, Tile.State state) extends Record
Represents a single (x,y) tile in a Maze.
